{"tid":430732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[屌孖妹]俄羅斯火辣兩姊妹列出嚇人要求徵老公！","createTime":"2017-10-10T05:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T05:47:09.000Z","uid":9888,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4731b57cba9e5bb35b32a510e0560245a457a699","tid":430732,"uid":9888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.addoil.com/men/290347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.addoil.com%2Fmen%2F290347&d=6EIVBcTCt3Z5UoWiU1NYWTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c6df26f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.addoil.com/men/290347</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/sister-preview-jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fsister-preview-jpg.jpg&h=1b4af48d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俄羅斯的中部地區喀山，住着一對美艷火辣的雙胞胎兩姊妹Adel Fakhteeva及Alina Fakhteeva，因為厭倦無聊的家鄉喀山，渴望有朝一日衝出光明之都莫斯科，異口同聲地表示徵求對象，更公開表明不介意二人共侍一夫，強調兩人不論任何事斬會在一起。<br />\n<br />\n目前仍在上大學的兩姊妹，現年22歲，共同經營時尚部落格，常在社交媒體發放二人的性感合照，而相中的二人更是穿上一模一樣的衣服，擺着類似的姿勢，因而在家鄉喀山薄有名氣。她們亦曾為不同品牌代言，每月可賺取約一萬盧布的收入（約1,350港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/sister-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fsister-2.jpg&h=d9e9de0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/sister-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fsister-3.jpg&h=1543de90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/sister-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fsister-4.jpg&h=1f86d789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/sister-5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fsister-5.jpg&h=d32cd717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/sister-6.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fsister-6.jpg&d=6EIVBcTCt3Z5UoWiU1NYWTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=806a16f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/sister-6.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/sister-7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fsister-7.jpg&h=9109d06a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://d361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net/joli100/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/sister-8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd361z6bv9zvbxb.cloudfront.net%2Fjoli100%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fsister-8.jpg&h=4829c2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n她們對「共享丈夫」的條件卻非常苛刻，除了思想開放，不會認為有兩個老婆是件怪事外，最重要的是，對象需要「有錢到嘔」（disgustingly rich）。<br />\n<br />\n她們可不是說說就算，她們已身體力行地聯絡當地商人和政治人物，希望他們可以幫忙。當地的前首長已答應會幫她們尋覓適合的老公人選，並會根據《福布斯》的俄羅斯富豪榜尋求願意提供協助的人。<br />\n<br />\n網民直斥兩姊妹的行為噁心，不明白為什麼有人會願意幫忙，也有人自稱是有錢人，毛遂自薦地應徵「共享丈夫」，似乎希望享受左右逢源的齊人之福！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea15e86d94ed70ca4af3415b8eddae4ba5740c0","tid":430732,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:22:31.000Z","msg":"起雙飛賣，識貨"},{"pid":"4dc58381a5eba551cca9889ad92ccfdff60aef0